As she knelt in front of Megatron, she looked at him. "I am yours to 
commanse Megatron.  All I have done, I did you bring glory to you and 
the Predacons.  But for my failure to kill the maximal who challenged 
me, I shall accept what ever punishment you deem suitable for me."  
She lowered her head and waited for the blow to come down on her.
